This task is to take a Natural Number in a given Base and return the sum of its digits:
:<code>1</code><sub><code>10</code></sub> sums to <math>1</math>;
:<code>1234</code><sub><code>10</code></sub> sums to <math>10</math>;
:<code>fe</code><sub><code>16</code></sub> sums to <math>29</math>;
:<code>f0e</code><sub><code>16</code></sub> sums to <math>29</math>.
